file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: test
servers:
  - url: /api/{version}:{name}
    variables:
      version:
        default: v1
        enum:
          - v1
          - v2
      name:
        default: petstore
        enum:
          - petstore
          - storeofpets
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      parameters: 
        - name: id
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: number
      responses:
        '200':
          description: response
